hopobject.body: Where are you calling from? etoricoxib 90 mg tablets World View Enterprises plans on sending tourists in to space by 2016 aboard high altitude balloons, all this for $75,000 only. They plan on sending six passengers and two crew members to a height of 18 miles above the Earth's surface from where they can view the magnificent curvature of the Earth against the black sky. The capsule will be suspended by a giant helium balloon. They will get the same view as astronauts but minus the weightlessness.
